{
 "translations": [
  {
   "offset": 10,
   "len": 26,
   "en": "a golden-haired young man.",
   "zh": "一位金髮燦爛之青年男子。",
   "note": "DESC"
  },
  {
   "offset": 51,
   "len": 46,
   "en": "\"Avatar! Good $T, $G! How has thy quest gone?\"",
   "zh": "「聖者！$T安，$G！試煉進展如何？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 98,
   "len": 31,
   "en": "\"Hey! The Avatar! Good $T, $G!\"",
   "zh": "「嘿！是聖者！$T安，$G！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 132,
   "len": 60,
   "en": "\"You've come to me to aid thee in thy quest! What an honor!\"",
   "zh": "「汝前來尋我助其試煉！榮幸之至！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 206,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"What else can I do for thee?\"",
   "zh": "「還有何處能效勞？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 243,
   "len": 48,
   "en": "\"I have a large inventory, so be more specific:\"",
   "zh": "「在下貨物繁多，請說具體些：」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 294,
   "len": 33,
   "en": "\"Dost thou want @arms or @armor?\"",
   "zh": "「汝要@arms（兵器）還是@armor（盔甲）？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 345,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Come by my shop when I'm open!\"",
   "zh": "「開店時歡迎光臨！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 409,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Come by my shop when I'm open!\"",
   "zh": "「開店時歡迎光臨！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 473,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Come by my shop when I'm open!\"",
   "zh": "「開店時歡迎光臨！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 522,
   "len": 89,
   "en": "\"Oh, I'm not important like you. I'm just a weaponsmith--and only a @journeyman at that.\"",
   "zh": "「哦，我哪比得上汝。我不過是個武器匠——而且只是個@journeyman中級匠師罷了。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 622,
   "len": 54,
   "en": "\"Aye, just a few years ago I was a simple apprentice.\"",
   "zh": "「是啊，幾年前我還只是個普通學徒。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 679,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"Now I @supply arms to all Trinsic!\"",
   "zh": "「如今我@supply（供應）整個特林希克的武器！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 726,
   "len": 54,
   "en": "\"My name's Brandon, $G, and I'm honored to meet thee!\"",
   "zh": "「在下布蘭登，$G，能與汝相識，榮幸之至！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 791,
   "len": 43,
   "en": "\"That would be a great honor! I'd love to!\"",
   "zh": "「那真是莫大榮幸！我十分樂意！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 837,
   "len": 28,
   "en": "The man comes to his senses.",
   "zh": "他回過神來。",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 868,
   "len": 62,
   "en": "\"But no, I can't. I've responsibilites here, especially @now.\"",
   "zh": "「但不行，我有責任在身，尤其是@now（眼）下這個時刻。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 961,
   "len": 27,
   "en": "\"And glad I am to hear it!\"",
   "zh": "「聽到此言甚感欣慰！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1003,
   "len": 54,
   "en": "\"I have to make @weapons to help fight the gargoyles!\"",
   "zh": "「我須打造@weapons（武器）以助抗擊魔像族！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1072,
   "len": 42,
   "en": "\"Farewell! May thy quest succeed, Avatar!\"",
   "zh": "「珍重！願汝試煉告捷，聖者！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1122,
   "len": 77,
   "en": "\"Perhaps you'd like to @buy some. I'd be honored to have thee as a customer.\"",
   "zh": "「或許汝有意@buy（買）？能以汝為主顧，榮幸之至。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1207,
   "len": 17,
   "en": "\"Beg pardon, $G?\"",
   "zh": "「$G，請再說一遍？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1373,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Sorry, none of you has anything I need.\"",
   "zh": "「抱歉，汝等所帶之物均非在下所需。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1449,
   "len": 38,
   "en": "\"Aye, $Y has something of interest...\"",
   "zh": "「啊，$Y帶有在下感興趣之物……」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1549,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「你們哪位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1786,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Which item?\" ",
   "zh": "「哪件物品？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1878,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"Will you take #7 gold for that $0, $Y?\" ",
   "zh": "「$Y，#7枚金幣換那件$0，意下如何？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1932,
   "len": 32,
   "en": "\"Perhaps some other time, then.\"",
   "zh": "「那便改日再談。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 1972,
   "len": 30,
   "en": "\"Perhaps something else then?\"",
   "zh": "「那別的物品如何？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2126,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"Changed your mind, eh?\"",
   "zh": "「改變主意了？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2238,
   "len": 16,
   "en": "\"Which of you?\" ",
   "zh": "「你們哪位？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2400,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Which item?\" ",
   "zh": "「哪件物品？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2482,
   "len": 24,
   "en": "\"That $1 costs #1 gold.\"",
   "zh": "「$1售價#1枚金幣。」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2509,
   "len": 14,
   "en": "\"Interested?\" ",
   "zh": "「有興趣否？」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2570,
   "len": 41,
   "en": "\"But 'twould make thee o'erburdened, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「然此舉將令汝負重過多，$Y！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2665,
   "len": 12,
   "en": "\"Excellent!\"",
   "zh": "「甚好！」",
   "note": ""
  },
  {
   "offset": 2740,
   "len": 36,
   "en": "\"But thou hast not enough gold, $Y!\"",
   "zh": "「然汝金幣不足，$Y！」",
   "note": ""
  }
 ],
